    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 4 Creation Points </p><p>Keyword: Weapon </p><p>Drain: 5 CCD Chakra </p><p></p><p>A large assault rifle that focuses fire as it ramps up its fire-rate.</p><p> As an action, you can spend the CCD Drain up to 5 times and select a creature within 60 feet of you.</p><p> You can make a ranged weapon attack for every 5 CCD chakra spent, dealing 1d6+1 force damage on each hit.</p><p> Each successful hit after the first on the same target adds a stacking +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with the X0-16 until the beginning of your next turn.</p><p></p>",
